  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA59">
<l>māṭē varappeṟuva rāmeṉṟē valviṉaiyār</l>
<l>kāṭāṉu mātāṉuṅ kaikoḷḷā rūṭēpōyp</l>
<l>pōrōtañ cintutiraik kaṇvaḷarum pērāḷaṉ</l>
<l>pērōtac cintikkap pērntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Thinking there will be their getting to come [back] to the place the harsh deeds</l>
<l>won’t take themselves in hand(?) in the forest or wherever – going in the middle</l>
<l>while [we?] retreat [and] think of reciting the names of the great man</l>
<l>who closes his eyes on the waves spilled by the battling flood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
